>Knowledge</p></div><p class="sc-59baed0b-10 gqsGJu">Frameworks</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-11 llxLtL">Knowledge is often a matter of discovery. But when the nature of an enquiry itself is at question, it is an act of creation</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-12 fuyVND cWJVNA">Céline Henne</p></div><div class="sc-59baed0b-6 dtyrwz"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/on-hope-philosophical-personalism-and-martin-luther-king-jr"><div class="sc-59baed0b-9 emuUeA"><div type="essay" class="sc-4c9ef492-2 eTKecW"><img alt="Black-and-white photo of three Black men sitting at a table with microphones during a press conference. One of the men has a bandage on his head." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/essay-final-nyc12794.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6f708321-f6cf-4da2-9aaf-fdcac679c2c1/es